        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat(cursor): show personal on-demand spend alongside team pool",
        "body": "Resolves #1622\n\n### Summary\nFor Cursor team plans, the usage summary payload includes both the shared team on-demand pool (`teamUsage.onDemand`) and the individual member's own on-demand spend (`individualUsage.onDemand`). CodexBar previously only exposed the team pool, losing visibility on the member's personal spend.\n\nThis PR:\n1. Adds `personalUsed` to `ProviderCostSnapshot` to carry the individual member's spend when a shared team budget/pool is headline.\n2. Updates `CursorStatusProbe` to parse the user's `individualUsage.onDemand.used` as `personalUsed` when the headline is the team pool.\n3. Renders a \"Your spend\" line beneath the team pool in the cost view (`MenuCardView`).\n4. Adds test coverage for team on-demand budget and personal spend in `CursorEnterpriseUsageTests`.",
